1
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:39,400
[Royal Feast]

2
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:43,620
[Episode 34]

3
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,000
Sir,

4
00:01:48,919 --> 00:01:49,720
Noble Consort Sun is here.

5
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,040
Eunuch Manager Yuan

6
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,000
doesn't look too good.

7
00:01:52,199 --> 00:01:53,279
You have to be careful.

8
00:01:56,839 --> 00:01:58,199
(Locusts may be small.)

9
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,839
(But they've caused a lot of damage.)

10
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,800
(They multiply easily.)

11
00:02:02,279 --> 00:02:03,760
(Yet, it's hard to exterminate them.)

12
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,919
(When the grains finally grow,)

13
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,839
(every field is lush green.)

14
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,960
(Every year during harvest time,)

15
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,119
(the locusts swarmed out of a sudden.)

16
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,360
(They ravaged the seedlings, plant nodes,)

17
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,320
(as well as the leaves and the spikes.)

18
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,479
(It hurts the cultivation of fields,)

19
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,639
(which is the life of the ordinary people.)

20
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:26,800
Your Majesty.

21
00:02:29,279 --> 00:02:29,919
I asked you here

22
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:31,039
to ask you about something.

23
00:02:31,679 --> 00:02:32,520
Do ask, Your Majesty.

24
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,279
Locusts plague

25
00:02:34,279 --> 00:02:35,320
Hejian, Shunde,

26
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,759
Shandong, and Shanxi.

27
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,679
Is that correct?

28
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:40,119
Your Majesty,

29
00:02:40,399 --> 00:02:41,199
locust plagues have occurred frequently

30
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,000
from the 4th to 7th month since the Hongwu Reign.

31
00:02:43,399 --> 00:02:44,800
The situation is most severe
in the summer and autumn.

32
00:02:45,119 --> 00:02:46,199
It's not the time of the year yet.

33
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,479
Hejian and Shunde may have a locust plague.

34
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:50,039
But due to the prefectures and counties'
local authorities' timely supervision

35
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:52,000
on the locals in catching
the locusts and growing millet.

36
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,320
Now, it's already under control.

37
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:55,199
Last year, the local authorities of Shandong

38
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,479
had been urging the farmers

39
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:58,039
to grow mulberry trees, taro,

40
00:02:58,479 --> 00:02:59,479
sesame, black beans, and more.

41
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,639
The locust plague may be serious.

42
00:03:01,119 --> 00:03:02,320
But the people can still make
a living to feed the family.

43
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,839
Only the prefecture of Shanxi fails

44
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,199
in exterminating the locusts.

45
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:06,759
The officials only did enough to get by,

46
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,160
which led to the crops being ravaged by locusts.

47
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,679
The people have little food to eat.

48
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,600
Yunzhou,

49
00:03:13,119 --> 00:03:15,759
I heard you flattered the Late Emperor

50
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:19,000
by criticizing the officials,
making them feel insecure,

51
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,440
which led to heated discussion.

52
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:21,600
Is that what happened?

53
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,479
I hope Your Majesty can forgive me

54
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:24,800
for speaking bluntly.

55
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,000
A bronze mirror

56
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,479
reflects the human heart.

57
00:03:30,399 --> 00:03:31,000
What's the difference

58
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,880
between good and evil?

59
00:03:33,279 --> 00:03:34,360
There are locust plagues in several places.

60
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,119
How much of the relief funds allocated

61
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,679
by the imperial court are used for disaster?

62
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,360
How many are unaccounted for?

63
00:03:40,679 --> 00:03:41,399
I've prepared the list of officials

64
00:03:41,399 --> 00:03:42,199
who handled the relief fund.

65
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:43,320
Please peruse, Your Majesty.

66
00:03:55,701 --> 00:03:58,025
[The Fifth Month of the First Year of Xuande Reign]
[Internal Investigation One]

67
00:03:59,839 --> 00:04:01,320
(I've been here all morning.)

68
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:03,399
(Why wait until the end of the year?)

69
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,320
(Heaven has mercy for the people.)

70
00:04:05,839 --> 00:04:07,240
(Man didn't cause it.)

71
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,039
(Think of the people's hardship and don't idle.)

72
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:11,039
(People who suffer are watching.)

73
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:13,000
(In ancient times, there were poems
on removing borers.)

74
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,360
(There were also officials catching locusts.)

75
00:04:15,839 --> 00:04:17,440
Exterminate the pests and aid the victims.

76
00:04:18,119 --> 00:04:19,600
The reviews of predecessors are prepared.

77
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,440
Save the people from fire and water,

78
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,480
and don't neglect your duties.

79
00:04:25,359 --> 00:04:26,480
I find these greedy officials

80
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,519
are much scarier than the locusts.

81
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:29,679
Order

82
00:04:29,679 --> 00:04:30,880
the imperial bodyguard to capture all of them.

83
00:04:31,279 --> 00:04:32,679
Execute those who deserve it.

84
00:04:33,799 --> 00:04:34,559
Pass this poem

85
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,600
to all officials.

86
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,679
Let them take this as a warning.

87
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,079
Yes, Your Majesty.

88
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:38,519
Your Highness,

89
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,480
I did offend you in the past.

90
00:05:42,359 --> 00:05:43,559
But things have changed now.

91
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,239
There's no need to be mindful

92
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,880
that you had to defame me

93
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,640
in front of His Majesty.

94
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,279
Officer You,

95
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:53,040
did I defame you,

96
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,640
or

97
00:05:55,239 --> 00:05:56,279
did you guise yourself too well

98
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:57,559
in front of His Majesty?

99
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,720
The current important official, Official Yang,

100
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,920
always behaved cautiously and respectfully

101
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,760
during Yongle Emperor's reign.

102
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,640
He dared not speak more than he should.

103
00:06:07,559 --> 00:06:08,920
But now, he's speaking without any restraint

104
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,079
of the current malpractices

105
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:10,959
in front of His Majesty.

106
00:06:12,119 --> 00:06:14,279
The Minister of Rites, Lyu Zhen,
is extremely good at flattering.

107
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,040
Now, he's also restraining himself from doing bad

108
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:16,959
and starts working seriously.

109
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,480
As the saying goes, the one on top

110
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,440
has a deep impact on those at the bottom.

111
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,480
I'm only doing what I was ordered to do.

112
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:23,119
What's wrong with that?

113
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,480
Officer You, please watch your words.

114
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,799
If someone else heard that,

115
00:06:27,119 --> 00:06:28,320
they'd think

116
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,279
you were criticizing

117
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,119
Yongle Emperor

118
00:06:31,119 --> 00:06:32,480
about what you've just said.

119
00:06:34,359 --> 00:06:35,279
What did you hear?

120
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:38,519
We heard

121
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,679
you said

122
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:42,519
Yongle Emperor was resolute

123
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,559
and decisive

124
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:46,040
while the current Emperor is open-minded

125
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,399
and readily follow good advice.

126
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,239
The imperial bodyguards
are the eyes and ears of His Majesty.

127
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,079
His Majesty would naturally trust me.

128
00:06:55,359 --> 00:06:56,359
As for you,

129
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,320
you should return to Yongning Palace

130
00:06:59,359 --> 00:07:00,760
and take good care of Yantai.

131
00:07:01,679 --> 00:07:03,440
I hope you'll remember what you said today.

132
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,480
You need to remember.

133
00:07:06,799 --> 00:07:08,040
His Majesty needs

134
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,359
ears and eyes that understand
the people's sufferings.

135
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,000
Let's go.

136
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,799
Noble Consort Sun

137
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,040
deliberately puts you in a difficult position.

138
00:07:43,679 --> 00:07:44,279
Fu Jiang.

139
00:07:50,239 --> 00:07:51,880
Dried persimmon can be replaced
with persimmon powder.

140
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:54,760
It's more effective in reducing phlegm
and treating cough.

141
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,519
I've already written

142
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,720
the lists

143
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,320
of restricted foods and drinks during meals.

144
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,600
Please

145
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,119
let Imperial Physician Sheng peruse it
before preparing them.

146
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,519
Thank you, Your Highness.

147
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,320
The four prefectures of Jinan, Yanzhou,

148
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:14,320
Dongchang, and Qingzhou

149
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,799
hadn't rained

150
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:17,720
since last year's 7th month.

151
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,320
The seedlings in the paddy field

152
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,519
had all wilted.

153
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,559
The people can't even feed themselves.

154
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,559
Yet, the Ministry of Works

155
00:08:23,559 --> 00:08:24,640
sends people to purchase ornaments?

156
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:25,959
What kind of ornaments

157
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:27,320
need to be bought this urgently?

158
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:28,640
Shaoyuan,

159
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,519
do you know about this?

160
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,239
Your Majesty,

161
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,440
the Ministry of Works sent people

162
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:35,799
to buy the ornaments are used

163
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,119
to build the mausoleum for our ancestors.

164
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,119
Mausoleum?

165
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,320
It's just a bunch of excuses.

166
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:42,960
Isn't the people of Shandong

167
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,200
the people of our ancestors too?

168
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,719
Our ancestors would be heartbroken

169
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,919
to see their people suffering.

170
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:50,960
Pass my order.

171
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,640
Halt all purchasing.

172
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,719
If they dare to cause trouble
for the people again,

173
00:08:55,359 --> 00:08:56,599
I'll execute them!

174
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,479
Yes, Your Majesty.

175
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,359
Is this also happening

176
00:09:00,119 --> 00:09:00,960
in other places?

177
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,320
Why didn't you report this to me?

178
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:10,840
Your Majesty.

179
00:09:17,359 --> 00:09:17,960
Never mind.

180
00:09:18,599 --> 00:09:20,039
Summon the Minister of Works into the palace now.

181
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,159
Yes, Your Majesty.

182
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,599
Greetings, Your Majesty and Your Highness.

183
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,280
Directress Yin,

184
00:09:42,119 --> 00:09:42,599
serve the dishes.

185
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,440
Yes, Your Highness.

186
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,239
Your Majesty, have some meal.

187
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,479
Do you smell anything,

188
00:09:54,479 --> 00:09:55,719
Your Majesty?

189
00:09:58,159 --> 00:09:59,919
I guess mint is better.

190
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,159
It's refreshing

191
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:04,039
and calming to the mind.

192
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:06,520
Directress Yin,

193
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:08,479
prepare mint tea

194
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,559
with some honey

195
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:11,719
for His Majesty tomorrow.

196
00:10:12,479 --> 00:10:13,440
His Majesty won't get angry easily

197
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,239
after drinking it.

198
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:16,520
Yes, Your Highness.

199
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,080
This smell

200
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:20,000
does have a calming effect.

201
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,239
It's too bad

202
00:10:21,239 --> 00:10:22,520
it was a gift from my betrothed.

203
00:10:23,159 --> 00:10:25,520
Otherwise, I would have given it to you.

204
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:27,840
When did you betroth?

205
00:10:28,479 --> 00:10:30,119
She's the eldest daughter of my teacher,

206
00:10:30,119 --> 00:10:31,239
Official Wang of Hanlin Academy.

207
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,599
It was decided last year.

208
00:10:33,239 --> 00:10:34,640
We've already picked an auspicious day
on the sixth month this year.

209
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,760
This dish looks familiar.

210
00:10:42,239 --> 00:10:42,880
This one

211
00:10:43,479 --> 00:10:46,200
is yellow croaker with imitation crab roe.

212
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,875
[Imitation Crab]

213
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:49,000
I can't eat crab since young.

214
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,880
But I like it so much.

215
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,919
That's why I kept asking Noble Consort Sun

216
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,840
about this.

217
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:54,359
When I reached home,

218
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:55,200
the cook at home

219
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,320
couldn't imitate the taste of crab at all.

220
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,000
I thought

221
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,119
I wouldn't be able to eat it anymore.

222
00:10:59,039 --> 00:10:59,559
Sir,

223
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:00,960
the secret in this dish

224
00:11:01,239 --> 00:11:02,559
doesn't use chicken egg yolk

225
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,080
but duck salted egg yolk

226
00:11:04,239 --> 00:11:05,559
that was soaked in brine and preserved

227
00:11:05,559 --> 00:11:06,359
with salted charcoal.

228
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,239
So it was duck's salted egg.

229
00:11:09,239 --> 00:11:10,000
Did I tell you

230
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,919
to join me for lunch?

231
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,239
Get back to work.

232
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,000
You're not going to have a single bite.

233
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,559
Directress Su takes great care

234
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:47,119
in preparing

235
00:11:47,119 --> 00:11:48,479
the Empress's meals every day.

236
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,479
But Kunning Palace would always send it back.

237
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:53,080
Has the Empress not recovered

238
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,119
from her cold yet?

239
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,200
After the Imperial Academy
of Medicine treatments,

240
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,080
the Empress's cold

241
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,159
had recovered greatly.

242
00:11:58,799 --> 00:11:59,640
It's just that her illness

243
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,359
had completely affected Her Majesty's appetite.

244
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,000
She no longer eats

245
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,880
her favorite dishes.

246
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:04,440
He Shu.

247
00:12:12,919 --> 00:12:13,640
Directress Yin,

248
00:12:14,119 --> 00:12:15,599
Her Majesty has ordered

249
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,520
that I'll be the one

250
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:17,679
preparing meals for Kunning Palace.

251
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,479
Everyone is only worried

252
00:12:19,479 --> 00:12:20,520
about Her Majesty's health.

253
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,640
If you need my help,

254
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:23,799
just ask me.

255
00:12:24,799 --> 00:12:25,559
Directress Yin,

256
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,239
are you going to meddle in this matter?

257
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:29,000
I didn't mean to interfere.

258
00:12:29,239 --> 00:12:30,080
-It's just...
-No need.

259
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,799
I'll change all the meal lists.

260
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:35,880
Why are you standing there?

261
00:13:00,119 --> 00:13:01,359
This matter is of great concern.

262
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,559
The Imperial Food Service

263
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:04,119
must report this to Empress Dowager.

264
00:13:05,119 --> 00:13:06,119
Kunning Palace has ordered

265
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,799
not to disclose the Empress's appetite

266
00:13:07,799 --> 00:13:09,080
to anyone.

267
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:11,320
But this year's Qianqiu Festival,

268
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:13,200
the Empress had exempted
the wives of the officials

269
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,320
from bringing gifts

270
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,440
because she wasn't well.

271
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:17,080
She's becoming thinner day by day.

272
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,799
The Empress Dowager
and the Emperor are very concerned,

273
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:20,679
and they've been asking about this.

274
00:13:21,799 --> 00:13:22,400
Moreover,

275
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:23,880
Empress Dowager will depart

276
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:25,200
to pay her respects at the Yongle Emperor's
and Hongxi Emperor's mausoleum.

277
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:26,799
Since they'll be traveling together.

278
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,400
How long can we hide this matter?

279
00:13:29,679 --> 00:13:30,520
It's my fault.

