00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:52,000
there are too many people

568
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,520
with unknown backgrounds.

569
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,199
If anything happens,

570
00:28:55,439 --> 00:28:57,199
my head would be on the line.

571
00:28:57,959 --> 00:28:59,239
So the Court of Imperial Entertainments

572
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:01,000
came here in advance yesterday.

573
00:29:01,439 --> 00:29:02,319
The kitchen servants from the palace

574
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,680
indeed made these flatbreads.

575
00:29:08,359 --> 00:29:08,880
Your Majesty,

576
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:11,920
your flatbread is better.

577
00:29:12,719 --> 00:29:13,959
It has more sesame seeds.

578
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:15,959
Can we switch?

579
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:19,640
Eunuch Yuan,

580
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,560
don't blame the cooks of the palace.

581
00:29:22,599 --> 00:29:23,839
They wouldn't dare

582
00:29:23,839 --> 00:29:25,079
to make common folks' flatbread.

583
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:27,040
They were just coping with it.

584
00:29:27,319 --> 00:29:28,400
His Majesty rarely has the chance

585
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:30,119
to try country dishes.

586
00:29:30,839 --> 00:29:31,439
How could

587
00:29:31,439 --> 00:29:32,599
he know?

588
00:29:37,040 --> 00:29:38,800
Mother, it's time to depart.

589
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:40,680
Let's go.

590
00:30:00,199 --> 00:30:00,719
Your Majesty,

591
00:30:03,719 --> 00:30:04,800
Prince of Wei is missing.

592
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:06,719
How did that happen?

593
00:30:06,959 --> 00:30:07,800
The servant reported

594
00:30:08,199 --> 00:30:09,040
that the Prince of Wei

595
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:10,439
went missing after relieving himself

596
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:11,079
as an excuse

597
00:30:11,079 --> 00:30:12,040
while everyone was resting.

598
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:13,520
I've already led the men

599
00:30:13,520 --> 00:30:14,280
and searched the farmhouse.

600
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,640
I've also ordered the palace guard
and imperial bodyguards

601
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,719
to expand the search area.

602
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:24,439
Your Majesty, it's time to go.

603
00:30:26,079 --> 00:30:27,479
I'm feeling hot now.

604
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:29,040
I'm going to get changed.

605
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,520
Attend Empress Dowager and return
to the temporary imperial abode first.

606
00:30:32,719 --> 00:30:33,920
Order the officials to go ahead before the rest.

607
00:30:34,319 --> 00:30:35,760
I'll wait there for an audience with them.

608
00:30:36,359 --> 00:30:36,800
Yes, Your Majesty.

609
00:30:37,079 --> 00:30:37,640
Yes, Your Majesty.

610
00:31:48,719 --> 00:31:49,239
Sir.

611
00:31:53,439 --> 00:31:53,959
Your Majesty,

612
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:55,959
Prince of Wei is up ahead.

613
00:31:56,520 --> 00:31:57,359
But...

614
00:31:57,439 --> 00:31:58,239
But what?

615
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,000
Noble Consort Sun insisted on joining.

616
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:10,680
Why are you here?

617
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,119
I'll go

618
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:15,599
wherever you go.

619
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:16,839
Outrageous. Guards!

620
00:32:17,239 --> 00:32:18,000
Send her back.

621
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,359
You know I have a loose tongue.

622
00:32:20,359 --> 00:32:21,959
What if I said something I shouldn't

623
00:32:22,439 --> 00:32:23,959
when I meet Empress Dowager?

624
00:32:24,280 --> 00:32:25,040
What would you do, then?

625
00:32:33,675 --> 00:32:35,050
[Animal on screen is CG]

626
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,719
I know horsemanship and archery at 13.

627
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:47,079
I went hunting with my father at 14.

628
00:32:47,959 --> 00:32:49,479
It's nothing difficult to catch a game or two.

629
00:32:50,199 --> 00:32:50,880
But

630
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:53,079
my skills had declined after staying
in the palace for a long time.

631
00:32:53,520 --> 00:32:54,359
That's why I missed it.

632
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:55,959
But it's all right.

633
00:32:56,319 --> 00:32:57,760
Your Majesty can take me
to your next hunting trip.

634
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,319
I'll naturally improve if I practice more.

635
00:33:05,599 --> 00:33:06,079
Chen Wu,

636
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:07,280
stay and take care of things.

637
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:08,640
Explain to Empress Dowager on my behalf.

638
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:09,439
Yes, Your Majesty.

639
00:33:28,760 --> 00:33:29,560
Your Majesty.

640
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:37,680
Huaping,

641
00:33:38,479 --> 00:33:40,280
did you see Chen Wu just now?

642
00:33:41,119 --> 00:33:42,040
Eunuch Chen?

643
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:43,719
Speaking of him,

644
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:44,719
where did he go?

645
00:33:47,959 --> 00:33:48,560
Something bad had happened.

646
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:10,560
Who told you to come here?

647
00:34:11,120 --> 00:34:12,360
Do you know how dangerous this is?

648
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:13,760
Tell me.

649
00:34:14,199 --> 00:34:14,600
Why did you

650
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:15,320
come here all by yourself?

651
00:34:16,199 --> 00:34:16,719
Speak.

652
00:34:20,479 --> 00:34:21,639
I forced the little eunuch

653
00:34:21,639 --> 00:34:22,840
to wear my clothes

654
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:24,399
and ride in the carriage,

655
00:34:24,479 --> 00:34:26,399
while I wore his clothes

656
00:34:26,399 --> 00:34:27,439
and came out here.

657
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:28,320
Your Highness,

658
00:34:28,879 --> 00:34:30,000
how did you manage to sneak out

659
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,040
with so many people watching?

660
00:34:32,520 --> 00:34:33,639
You even came here all by yourself.

661
00:34:34,080 --> 00:34:34,879
That doesn't make sense.

662
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:42,280
It's up to you if you believe me or not.

663
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,479
My mother is no longer here anyway.

664
00:34:43,479 --> 00:34:44,679
Father is the same too.

665
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:45,479
No one in this world

666
00:34:45,479 --> 00:34:46,800
cares about me anymore.

667
00:34:46,919 --> 00:34:47,840
Nonsense.

668
00:34:48,439 --> 00:34:49,560
You're my brother.

669
00:34:50,399 --> 00:34:51,320
No matter what happens,

670
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:53,639
I'll always protect you.

671
00:34:54,919 --> 00:34:55,600
Big Brother,

672
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:57,040
everyone ignores me.

673
00:34:57,239 --> 00:34:57,719
I thought

674
00:34:57,719 --> 00:34:59,639
you didn't want me.

675
00:35:03,679 --> 00:35:04,679
Why would I come looking for you

676
00:35:05,560 --> 00:35:07,080
if I didn't care about you?

677
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:10,439
I'm worried

678
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:11,439
that you refuse to listen to them

679
00:35:11,439 --> 00:35:12,320
and come back.

680
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:13,600
Big Brother,

681
00:35:13,719 --> 00:35:15,199
you must promise

682
00:35:15,439 --> 00:35:16,959
that you won't hit me

683
00:35:16,959 --> 00:35:18,159
and scold me when we go back.

684
00:35:18,479 --> 00:35:19,000
All right.

685
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:21,719
But first, you must tell me

686
00:35:21,719 --> 00:35:22,919
who told you to do this.

687
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:23,959
Otherwise,

688
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:26,239
you'll have to copy
the ancestral instructions 500 times.

689
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:27,520
It was her.

690
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:32,879
Your Majesty,

691
00:35:33,719 --> 00:35:34,320
look.

692
00:35:36,439 --> 00:35:37,639
Who are those people?

693
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,639
Yunzhou, go and ask them.

694
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,080
Do we need to make a move now?

695
00:36:12,719 --> 00:36:13,399
There are many people.

696
00:36:13,479 --> 00:36:14,520
Things will go wrong easily.

697
00:36:15,080 --> 00:36:15,679
We'll wait a little longer.

698
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:23,560
Noble Consort Sun, what's wrong with my brother?

699
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:34,080
Your Majesty.

700
00:36:37,479 --> 00:36:38,280
Tell the truth.

701
00:36:40,719 --> 00:36:41,719
I've asked them.

702
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:42,399
Some are

703
00:36:42,399 --> 00:36:43,560
from Laishui County of Baoding Prefecture,

704
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:44,439
while some are

705
00:36:44,439 --> 00:36:45,560
from Xinhe County of Zhending Prefecture.

706
00:36:45,959 --> 00:36:47,439
Last year's drought caused a poor harvest.

707
00:36:47,639 --> 00:36:48,760
There was a locust plague this year

708
00:36:48,879 --> 00:36:49,800
with no crop to harvest.

709
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,919
Many people are fleeing to the capital.

710
00:37:01,959 --> 00:37:03,199
Wherever I go,

711
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:06,000
the people live and work in peace

712
00:37:07,239 --> 00:37:08,199
and content.

713
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:11,280
Everyone wishes me a long life wherever I go.

714
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:12,719
Little did I know

715
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,439
that the refugees

716
00:37:14,439 --> 00:37:15,800
were driven out here.

717
00:37:17,560 --> 00:37:18,280
Great.

718
00:37:19,439 --> 00:37:20,280
They're keeping the truth from me.

719
00:37:22,479 --> 00:37:23,560
How did you know?

720
00:37:25,679 --> 00:37:26,320
Me?

721
00:37:28,399 --> 00:37:29,199
Didn't you use Prince of Wei

722
00:37:29,199 --> 00:37:30,239
to bring me here,

723
00:37:31,399 --> 00:37:32,399
so I could see

724
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:34,280
how I was deceived and deceiving myself?

725
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:40,560
Your Majesty,

726
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:44,439
it was either drought or locust plague

727
00:37:44,919 --> 00:37:46,080
that affect Wei County of Guangping Prefecture

728
00:37:46,879 --> 00:37:48,560
and Bazhou of Shuntian Prefecture this year.

729
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,800
There are refugees all over the capital.

730
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,800
The people in the palace know about this.

731
00:37:55,439 --> 00:37:56,439
They're all hiding it from Your Majesty.

732
00:37:57,919 --> 00:37:58,840
You could've told me

733
00:37:58,840 --> 00:37:59,959
if you wanted me to know the truth.

734
00:38:00,959 --> 00:38:02,399
Yet, you want me to see it for myself.

735
00:38:03,239 --> 00:38:04,399
It's heart-wrenching.

736
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:06,679
Does it make you feel good to see me like this?

737
00:38:07,439 --> 00:38:08,959
If you don't see it yourself,

738
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:10,879
I won't know

739
00:38:11,439 --> 00:38:13,199
where they will drive those refugees away.

740
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,479
There will be no proof when that time comes.

741
00:38:17,439 --> 00:38:18,159
I'm afraid

742
00:38:18,679 --> 00:38:19,959
it'll be treated as a matter of course

743
00:38:20,959 --> 00:38:22,280
as that flatbread.

744
00:38:23,719 --> 00:38:24,719
When you were young,

745
00:38:25,439 --> 00:38:26,639
you followed Yongle Emperor

746
00:38:26,639 --> 00:38:27,919
to make secret visits to the people.

747
00:38:28,159 --> 00:38:29,320
You know people's hardships very well.

748
00:38:29,959 --> 00:38:30,760
You didn't mind

749
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:31,679
because

750
00:38:31,679 --> 00:38:32,959
those eunuchs were playing some tricks.

751
00:38:33,199 --> 00:38:33,800
To you,

752
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,000
it's not even worth mentioning.

753
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:37,560
Food, drinks,

754
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:38,840
purchasing, and filial piety.

755
00:38:39,120 --> 00:38:40,320
None of these are trivial matters.

756
00:38:41,959 --> 00:38:43,159
Even a dike as long

757
00:38:44,439 --> 00:38:45,439
as thousands of li

758
00:38:45,439 --> 00:38:46,879
can be slowly eaten away by ants.

759
00:38:52,120 --> 00:38:53,199
It's my fault.

760
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:56,439
Forgive me for my negligence, Your Majesty.

761
00:38:57,479 --> 00:38:58,439
You didn't neglect your duties.

762
00:39:00,120 --> 00:39:01,120
There was nothing you could do anyway.

763
00:39:01,879 --> 00:39:03,199
One slight move may affect the whole situation.

764
00:39:04,919 --> 00:39:05,959
If you said it,

765
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,679
you'd be criticizing me publicly.

766
00:39:16,479 --> 00:39:17,679
Big Brother, I'm hungry.

767
00:39:17,679 --> 00:39:18,919
I want to eat something.

768
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:20,840
Your Majesty,

769
00:39:21,560 --> 00:39:22,879
I've prepared some meals

770
00:39:23,239 --> 00:39:24,280
at the farmhouse just now.

771
00:39:25,479 --> 00:39:26,679
Why don't we eat

772
00:39:26,679 --> 00:39:28,080
before we return
to the temporary imperial abode?

773
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:38,239
You said you were helping me

774
00:39:38,239 --> 00:39:39,719
to test how much my brother loves me.

775
00:39:40,239 --> 00:39:41,679
You were lying to me.

776
00:39:42,040 --> 00:39:42,760
You're such

777
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:44,239
a scheming woman.

778
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:47,040
You deserve to lose his favor.

779
00:39:52,959 --> 00:39:53,439
Your Highness,

780
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:56,120
you can take my horse.

781
00:39:58,120 --> 00:40:00,679
This fine steed has a fierce temperament.

782
00:40:01,959 --> 00:40:02,840
It's been a while since I've ridden a horse.

783
00:40:03,520 --> 00:40:04,719
I'm afraid I can't handle it.

784
00:40:05,439 --> 00:40:06,080
You won't fall

785
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:07,479
with me around.

786
00:40:09,159 --> 00:40:09,840
Thank you.

787
00:40:15,639 --> 00:40:16,320
Sir,

788
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,879
how do I get back?

789
00:40:17,959 --> 00:40:18,600
Walk.

790
00:40:34,959 --> 00:40:35,439
You better not think

791
00:40:35,439 --> 00:40:36,439
that this will disperse my anger.

792
00:40:36,879 --> 00:40:37,919
I won't fall for this trick.

793
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:46,120
Big Brother, look.

794
00:40:53,120 --> 00:40:55,199
I went searching for the Prince of Wei.

795
00:40:59,719 --> 00:41:01,040
I've reported to Mother

796
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,280
that you were not happy

797
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:04,159
with what happened earlier.

798
00:41:04,879 --> 00:41:05,600
So you've decided

799
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,199
to visit

800
00:41:06,199 --> 00:41:07,560
the nearby villages personally.

801
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:09,439
Only then did Mother feel relieved

802
00:41:09,439 --> 00:41:10,679
and depart for the temporary imperial abode
to wait for our return.

803
00:41:11,719 --> 00:41:13,000
You must not have eaten.

804
00:41:13,639 --> 00:41:15,199
I've brought Directress Su with me.

805
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,520
Go and prepare the meals now.

806
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:18,800
Yes, Your Majesty.

807
00:41:27,600 --> 00:41:29,800
I was worried about the lack of help.

808
00:41:30,280 --> 00:41:31,120
Your Majesty,

809
00:41:31,120 --> 00:41:32,080
you're very thoughtful.

810
00:41:34,239 --> 00:41:34,800
Since it's rare

811
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,439
for us to be outside the palace,

812
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,479
why don't we try something new?

813
00:41:39,600 --> 00:41:40,159
Is that all right?

814
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:46,360
Ziping.

815
00:41:53,120 --> 00:41:53,600
Yunzhou,

816
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:55,199
have a seat.

817
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,040
Thank you for grace, Your Majesty.

818
00:42:19,760 --> 00:42:21,080
Your Highness, you mustn't.

819
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,159
Let me do it.

820
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:23,840
His Majesty

821
00:42:24,600 --> 00:42:25,000
has said

822
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:26,479
no need to restrain ourselves
while we were outside.

823
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:27,840
Let me do it.

824
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,560
I want to check the kitchen.

825
00:42:55,120 --> 00:42:55,800
Directress Yin,

826
00:42:57,159 --> 00:42:58,919
what is

827
00:42:59,159 --> 00:43:00,320
Directress Su making?

828
00:43:04,520 --> 00:43:05,600
If you mince it,

829
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:07,120
you'll have to remove the residue slowly later.

830
00:43:07,600 --> 00:43:08,439
Doing so can retain

831
00:43:08,439 --> 00:43:09,959
the original flavor of the chicken.

832
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:14,199
Get back to work.

833
00:43:42,479 --> 00:43:43,320
This is chicken congee.

834
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:44,024
[Chicken Congee]

835
00:43:47,959 --> 00:43:48,399
Here.

836
00:43:49,600 --> 00:43:50,159
You can have mine.

837
00:44:11,879 --> 00:44:12,679
It's tasty.

838
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:14,000
It's just too hot.
